  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00001",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "爰爰道人上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "自家名唤爰爰，修炼道气完全。也会餐霞吸露，也会拜斗谈元。才得人形略似，便从二窟乔迁。今日是非寂寞，喜遇二位英贤。一位夫人白骨，一位黄袍大仙。二人神通广大，仗他一点道元。略略显些灵验，顷刻盖造幡轩。特邀黄袍神圣，同去受享祭筵。",
      "text_length": 112
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "言犹未了，黄袍大仙早到。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众小妖引黄袍大仙同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "粉蝶儿",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "蓄养先天，俺可也蓄养先天。苦修来，体轻身健，只差些面靛毛拳。怪狰狞，光闪烁双睛如电，吼一声鬼怪神惊，叨居了紫金宫殿。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "脸面红须赤发飘，黄金铠甲日光摇。里肚衬腰青玉带，攀胸勒甲绿云绦。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "俺，黄袍大仙是也。爰爰道人，某听你言：福庇这安乐镇，居民受某许多德泽，并无一些祭敬，是何意思？想是你都侵食了。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "这怎么敢？爰爰偷嘴，不过小意思。怎敢大弄神通，欺瞒大王？今日庙宇完工，众乡民备着猪羊果品，彩亭鼓乐，迎送进庙。特来请大王赴会。",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "如此可请你新姐姐白骨夫人，同往受享。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "去不得。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "怎么去不得？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "养了孩儿了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "这又奇了。她又没丈夫，这是哪里来的？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰夫人"
      ],
      "text": "不知怎么摆弄出来的。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你休得取笑。既要在我门下，须要脸面些。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄袍大仙下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "真是好笑。如今世上男女，不顾脸面的很多，倒叫我妖怪顾脸面。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "爰爰道人下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众乡民抬彩亭、闻仁同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "众乡亲，不得听信妖人之言。倘官府知道，祸连一方，不是玩的。请早休息，各务生理。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "前日有一人在庙里乱道几句话，霎时间七窍流血死了。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "众乡亲，容小生一言。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "爰爰道人暗上。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "尊声列位听吾言，三教本是正宗传。愚民若被狂言煽，抛去本业不安全。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "你们不知厉害哩！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "王章三尺垂邦宪，妖道旁门乱胡言。料尔皈依难比佛，即速归正莫迟延。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "贫道不过替天行道，先生何用执迷。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "你是哪里妖道，到我这里来蛊惑众人么！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "替天行道我不信，蛊惑众人是真情。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "神圣感应，不受阴愆，定遭王法。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "神圣威灵原有惑，讲甚王法与阴愆。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "你若狂言，敢去对神面讲？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "我正要前去，数他几句！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "相公，不是玩耍的，去不得！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "正要前去当面讲，昌黎曾祭又何妨！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "你是何处木鬼山魈，敢来俺镇上兴妖作怪？你如今若能降下一阵风雪，我信你是位正神。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "神灵，这相公不信你的显应，你可速显威灵，步云降雨。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "相公要的是风雪。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "要风雪么，这又何难！速降，降！吾奉太上老君急急如律勅。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "爰爰道人低声。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "黄袍爷爷，黄袍祖宗，黄袍老官，没有风雪，也弄阵子雨来。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "妖怪，俺如今在此挺身，任你施为罢！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "快捆起狂生来，存些脸面，神圣爷爷！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "你这道人，不是相公正气冲散，我们被你迷惑几时是了！列位，打这妖道！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众乡民打爰爰道人下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "今日这坛祭筵，亏得相公识出底细，竟然打散了。但不知什么爰爰道人。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00047",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "列位不知，他取的名儿，却见于《诗经》上边。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00048",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "怎么讲？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00049",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "“有兔爰爰，雉离于罗”。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00050",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "若非相公指破群迷，我们怎得脱他罗网。请上，容我们拜谢。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00051",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。列位将这庙宇，改为乡约所。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00052",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "相公就是张道陵，能降妖怪。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00053",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "乡民甲"
      ],
      "text": "不是张道陵，倒是一位有识之士。张道陵降魔要符咒，相公降魔只动口。可不道：",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00054",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "乡民甲"
      ],
      "text": "宁动知识手，不动知识口。相公方动口，妖怪就出丑。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00055",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众乡民同笑。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00056",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众乡民"
      ],
      "text": "是吓。相公请！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00057",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00058",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "爰爰道人跑上。黄袍大仙赶上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00059",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "我正在作难，偏偏我的黄袍祖宗，你方才哪里去了？为何不似往日显圣了？弄我出这场大丑。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00060",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "大丑？你这小丑，你不知道往日显圣，只好吓那班村夫俗子。闻生是个正人，他乃文曲星降凡，魁光射斗，我怎么近得他？",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00061",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "虽然如此，你方才出门时，吩咐我存些体面，你自己不顾脸面了。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00062",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你我道行有限，脸面怎么顾得来？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00063",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "一场好事遭他贬，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00064",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你去请了白骨夫人。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00065",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "text": "同我去宝象国法力施展。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00066",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "爰爰道人"
      ],
      "text": "且住，近日出此大丑，闻生这口气，怎么出得？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006033_e00067",
      "play_id": "02006033",
      "scene_id": "02006033_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
